{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Tujrqgdg5itFRUvqCZ24aD","type":"tool_result","content":"@rng-utopia/lord-of-rngs:lint: \n@rng-utopia/chart-the-course:lint: cache hit, replaying logs 37049b19103cb298\n@rng-utopia/coinflip:lint: cache hit, replaying logs 316f74ba6dd7295a\n@rng-utopia/chart-the-course:lint: \n@rng-utopia/chart-the-course:lint: > @rng-utopia/chart-the-course@0.1.0 lint /workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/chart-the-course\n@rng-utopia/chart-the-course:lint: > eslint .\n@rng-utopia/chart-the-course:lint: \n@rng-utopia/coinflip:lint: \n@rng-utopia/coinflip:lint: > @rng-utopia/coinflip@0.1.0 lint /workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/coinflip\n@rng-utopia/coinflip:lint: > eslint .\n@rng-utopia/coinflip:lint: \n@rng-utopia/platform:lint: \n@rng-utopia/platform:lint: > @rng-utopia/platform@0.1.0 lint /workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform\n@rng-utopia/platform:lint: > eslint .\n@rng-utopia/platform:lint: \n@rng-utopia/platform:lint: \n@rng-utopia/platform:lint: /workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/boss-raid/components/BossRaidModal.tsx\n@rng-utopia/platform:lint:   76:6  warning  React Hook useEffect has a missing dependency: 'handleClose'. Either include it or remove the dependency array  react-hooks/exhaustive-deps\n@rng-utopia/platform:lint:   90:6  warning  React Hook useEffect has a missing dependency: 'handleClose'. Either include it or remove the dependency array  react-hooks/exhaustive-deps\n@rng-utopia/platform:lint: \n@rng-utopia/platform:lint: /workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/boss-raid/utils/mock-simulation.ts\n@rng-utopia/platform:lint:   432:5  warning  Unexpected console statement. Only these console methods are allowed: warn, error  no-console\n@rng-utopia/platform:lint: \n@rng-utopia/platform:lint: /workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/close-call/components/Candlestic